high_descs: Go straight, left, and then right to stand in front of the stove.
Pick the pot up on the bottom left of the stove.
Turn and stand in front of the sink.
Put the pot in the sink, turn the water off and then on and take the pot out of the sink.
Turn and face the stove with the pot in hand.
Put the pot on the lower left burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on the stove.

high_descs: Move forward, turn left and walk toward the counter, then turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pan in the front on the stove.
Turn left and walk forward then turn right to face the sink.
Wash the pot in the sink.
Turn right to face the stove.
Place the pot back on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Clean the pot on the front of the stove.

high_descs: Walk straight ahead then turn left at the counter. Walk towards the toaster, then turn right and walk towards the stove.
Pick up the metal pan closest to you.
Turn left, then place the pan in the sink
Turn on the faucet so water fills the sink. Turn off the water and pick up the pan again.
Turn right to face the stove again.
Place the pan on the stove where you originally found it.
anns.task_desc: Find and clean a pan before placing it back on the stove.
